documentation.text:
@notice Returns the amount out received for a given exact input but for a swap of a single pool
 @param params The params for the quote, encoded as `QuoteExactInputSingleParams`
 tokenIn The token being swapped in
 tokenOut The token being swapped out
 fee The fee of the token pool to consider for the pair
 amountIn The desired input amount
 limitSqrtP The price limit of the pool that cannot be exceeded by the swap

@notice Returns the amount in required to receive the given exact output amount but for a swap of a single pool
 @param params The params for the quote, encoded as `QuoteExactOutputSingleParams`
 tokenIn The token being swapped in
 tokenOut The token being swapped out
 fee The fee of the token pool to consider for the pair
 amountOut The desired output amount
 limitSqrtP The price limit of the pool that cannot be exceeded by the swap

devdoc.details: These functions are not marked view because they rely on calling non-view functions and reverting to compute the result. They are also not gas efficient and should not be called on-chain.

params.amountIn: The amount of the first token to swap
params.path: The path of the swap, i.e. each token pair and the pool fee

returns.afterSqrtPList: List of the sqrt price after the swap for each pool in the path
returns.amountOut: The amount of the last token that would be received
returns.gasEstimate: The estimate of the gas that the swap consumes
returns.initializedTicksCrossedList: List of the initialized ticks that the swap crossed for each pool in the path

params.params: The params for the quote, encoded as `QuoteExactInputSingleParams` tokenIn The token being swapped in tokenOut The token being swapped out fee The fee of the token pool to consider for the pair amountIn The desired input amount limitSqrtP The price limit of the pool that cannot be exceeded by the swap

params.amountOut: The amount of the last token to receive
params.path: The path of the swap, i.e. each token pair and the pool fee. Path must be provided in reverse order

returns.afterSqrtPList: List of the sqrt price after the swap for each pool in the path
returns.amountIn: The amount of first token required to be paid
returns.gasEstimate: The estimate of the gas that the swap consumes
returns.initializedTicksCrossedList: List of the initialized ticks that the swap crossed for each pool in the path
